## orthoDB ###
orthoDBspecies="" #one of : "Metazoa" "Vertebrata" "Viridiplantae" "Arthropoda" "Eukaryota" "Fungi" "Alveolata"
#if a species is given then it will be used for annotation (in addition to eventual RNAseq and orthProteins) 

